    "major_stream_name": "Arts",
    "like_dislike_summary": {
      "pos_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "Everyone of our college can issue their library cards. It is so much beneficial for the students whom are facing financial problems. They can pick free books from here, and lots of stocks are there. Also our college is famous for annual fest in bwn.",
          "name": "Rupam Mishra",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Our annual function are really very much amusing. Every year our college brings good artists of bollywood and other. All the departments and hostels make their stalls. You can enjoy 3 day full enjoyment in every year",
          "name": "Rupam Mishra",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Many rooms , hostel also there , so nothing about worry ,and all feselitis there in my college",
          "name": "Supriyo Das",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "And college principal and sir , mams are so good not rudely, behaviour so soft I like that",
          "name": "Supriyo Das",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "The campus of the college and it has a big play ground.",
          "name": "Sneharghya saha",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "The practical was conducted very well.Coding was practiced thoroughly in the lab.",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "BCA {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "They were taught well before the project was given.",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "BCA {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Fees",
          "name": "Alamin Mondal",
          "course_tag_name": "BA {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Well cooked and the price of the food of canteen",
          "name": "Arup Dan",
          "course_tag_name": "BA {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "Biggest campus in Burdwan. And you will going to like it if you see on your own",
          "name": "Deb Dwaipayan Biswas",
          "course_tag_name": "BCA {Hons.}"
        }
      ],
      "neg_sentences": [
        {
          "text": "If you are staying at hostel, you can face several problems in hostel. Sometimes college didi not provide proper goods for hostel facilities. The boarders of the hostel need to complaint for a long to have those things",
          "name": "Rupam Mishra",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "Sometimes the colleges under BU faces problems  on exam timing and results declaration",
          "name": "Rupam Mishra",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com"
        },
        {
          "text": "In this college junior member means they are servent for senior",
          "name": "Supriyo Das",
          "course_tag_name": "BA"
        },
        {
          "text": "No placements are given. No placements have been received.",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "BCA {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "No extra facilities provided .The building is very old. No new developments.",
          "name": "College Ninja",
          "course_tag_name": "BCA {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The registration process is very time taking and ridiculous.",
          "name": "Rupam Aditya",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "There's no gym , no wifi , no infrastructure improvement,no canteen ,no id card, no freshers no farewell. Typically a college which has it's name for it's last achievements but in this day it is a total useless college.",
          "name": "Rupam Aditya",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "The fees structure can be reduced shortly, because everyone can not effort the fees, so this is one of a thing I dislike",
          "name": "Biswajit Das",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Sc"
        },
        {
          "text": "I need to improve the college lab facility",
          "name": "Sautav panja",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        },
        {
          "text": "I am also dislike the location of the college.",
          "name": "Sautav panja",
          "course_tag_name": "B.Com {Hons.}"
        }
      ]
    },
